"title": "1175: God, will of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1175",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The intent and purpose of God, as revealed in Scripture. God's will for his creation and his people is set out in the Law and the Prophets, which find their fulfilment in Jesus Christ. A central aspect of the will of God is that his people be faithful and obedient.</p>\n<h2>The revelation of God's will</h2>\n<h3>In his word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:16\">2TI 3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:21\">2SA 7:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr17:19\">1CH 17:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:20-Ps103:21\">PSA 103:20–103:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:25-Col1:26\">COL 1:25–1:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:4-1John2:5\">1JN 2:4–2:5</a></p>\n<h3>Through the law</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:15-Exod18:16\">EXO 18:15–18:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:12\">EXO 24:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:16\">DEU 30:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:43\">PSA 119:43</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:12\">ROM 7:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:8\">1TI 1:8</a></p>\n<h3>Through the prophets</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:6-1Kgs22:7\">1KI 22:6–22:7</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr18:5-2Chr18:6\">2CH 18:5–18:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs3:11\">2KI 3:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer42:3-Jer42:4\">JER 42:3–42:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek12:25\">EZK 12:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos3:7\">AMO 3:7</a></p>\n<h3>In the apostolic gospel</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:27\">ACT 20:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:11-Gal1:12\">GAL 1:11–1:12</a></p>\n<h2>The fulfilment of God's will</h2>\n<h3>God's will is fulfilled in Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:9-Eph1:10\">EPH 1:9–1:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:4-Eph3:11\">EPH 3:4–3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:27\">COL 1:27</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ obeyed his Father's will</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:38\">JHN 6:38</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:39\">MAT 26:39</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:36\">MRK 14:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:42\">LUK 22:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:34\">JHN 4:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:30\">JHN 5:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:7\">HEB 10:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:8\">PSA 40:8</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's death fulfilled God's will</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:3-Gal1:4\">GAL 1:3–1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:10\">ISA 53:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:23\">ACT 2:23</a></p>\n<h2>God's will for the world</h2>\n<h3>God desires justice and righteousness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:24\">AMO 5:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:5\">PSA 33:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:7\">ISA 5:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:24\">JER 9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:8\">MIC 6:8</a></p>\n<h3>God desires honesty and truth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:22\">PRO 12:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:16\">EXO 20:16</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:20\">DEU 5:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:35-Lev19:36\">LEV 19:35–19:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:1\">PRO 11:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:16-Zech8:17\">ZEC 8:16–8:17</a></p>\n<h3>God desires harmony and peace</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:2-1Tim2:3\">1TI 2:2–2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:3-Isa2:4\">ISA 2:3–2:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:2-Mic4:3\">MIC 4:2–4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:6-Isa11:9\">ISA 11:6–11:9</a></p>\n<h3>God desires the world to be saved</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:4\">1TI 2:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:23\">EZK 18:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:11\">EZK 33:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:14\">MAT 18:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16-John3:17\">JHN 3:16–3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:9\">2PE 3:9</a></p>\n<h2>God's will for his redeemed people</h2>\n<h3>God desires loving obedience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:35-Matt22:38\">MAT 22:35–22:38</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:28-Mark12:29\">MRK 12:28–12:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:27\">LUK 10:27</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:5\">DEU 6:5</a>PSA <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut51:16-Deut51:17\">51:16–51:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:11\">ISA 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:22-Jer7:23\">JER 7:22–7:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:5\">1JN 2:5</a></p>\n<h3>God desires worship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9\">1PE 2:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps100:4\">PSA 100:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:23\">ISA 45:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:18\">1TH 5:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:6\">REV 1:6</a></p>\n<h3>God desires holiness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:3\">1TH 4:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:1-Lev19:2\">LEV 19:1–19:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:2\">1CO 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:22\">COL 1:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:7\">1TH 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:10\">HEB 10:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:15-1Pet1:16\">1PE 1:15–1:16</a></p>\n<h3>God desires love for one another</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:34-John13:35\">JHN 13:34–13:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:18\">LEV 19:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:39\">MAT 22:39</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:31\">MRK 12:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:27\">LUK 10:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:12-John15:13\">JHN 15:12–15:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:14\">GAL 5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:11\">1JN 3:11</a></p>\n<h3>God desires high moral standards</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:15\">1PE 2:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:16\">MAT 5:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:48\">MAT 5:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:4\">1PE 3:4</a></p>\n<h3>God's will may involve suffering</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:17\">1PE 3:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:22\">ACT 14:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:13-Acts21:14\">ACT 21:13–21:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:5-Heb12:7\">HEB 12:5–12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:19\">1PE 4:19</a></p>\n<h2>Proper responses to God's will</h2>\n<h3>Discovering God's will</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:17\">EPH 5:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:18\">ROM 2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:9\">COL 1:9</a></p>\n<h3>Obeying God's will</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:21\">MAT 7:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra10:11\">EZR 10:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:50\">MAT 12:50</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:35\">MRK 3:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:6\">EPH 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:21\">HEB 13:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:15\">JAS 4:15</a></p>\n<h3>Praying for God's will</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:10\">MAT 6:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps143:10\">PSA 143:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:42\">MAT 26:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:13-John14:14\">JHN 14:13–14:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:14\">1JN 5:14</a></p>\n<h3>Making radical changes to do God's will</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:2\">ROM 12:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:5\">ROM 8:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:16-Gal5:17\">GAL 5:16–5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:20\">JAS 1:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:14\">1PE 1:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:2\">1PE 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:15-1John2:17\">1JN 2:15–2:17</a></p>\n<h2>Rejecting God's will</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:30\">LUK 7:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:11\">PSA 107:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:1\">ISA 30:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:7\">EZK 3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:37\">MAT 23:37</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:34\">LUK 13:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:44\">JHN 8:44</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of people who obeyed God's will</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:21\">DEU 33:21</a> <em>Gad</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:14\">1SA 13:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:22\">ACT 13:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:36\">ACT 13:36</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:28-Isa45:1\">ISA 44:28–45:1</a> <em>Cyrus</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:21\">ACT 18:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:14\">ACT 21:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:10\">ROM 1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:32\">ROM 15:32</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:19\">1CO 4:19</a></p>\n<h2>Ways of discovering God's will</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:20\">EXO 18:20</a> <em>teaching</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:30\">EXO 28:30</a> <em>Urim and Thummim</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:11\">PSA 86:11</a> <em>prayer</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:105\">PSA 119:105</a> <em>God's word</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:22-Dan2:23\">DAN 2:22–2:23</a> <em>revelation</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:26\">JHN 14:26</a> <em>the Holy Spirit</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:26\">ACT 1:26</a> <em>drawing lots</em></p>\n<h2>God's will and the human will</h2>\n<h3>God's will overrules human wills</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:21\">PRO 19:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:10-Ps33:11\">PSA 33:10–33:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:9\">PRO 16:9</a></p>\n<h3>God's will overrides the desires of the wicked</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen50:20\">GEN 50:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:5-Isa10:11\">ISA 10:5–10:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:5-Hab1:11\">HAB 1:5–1:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:23\">ACT 2:23</a></p>\n<h3>God's will can harmonise with human wills</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr13:2\">1CH 13:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:4\">PSA 37:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:19\">PSA 145:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:28\">ACT 15:28</a></p>\n<h2>God's will is sovereign</h2>\n<h3>Over all things</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:11\">EPH 1:11</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Over creation</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:29\">MAT 10:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:20\">ROM 8:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:11\">REV 4:11</a></p>\n<h3>Over evil</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen45:8\">GEN 45:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:25\">1SA 2:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:4\">PRO 16:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:12\">ISA 65:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:18\">ROM 9:18</a></p>\n<h3>Over the gospel</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:18\">MIC 7:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:25-Matt11:26\">MAT 11:25–11:26</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:21\">LUK 10:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:21\">JHN 5:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:48\">ACT 13:48</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:18\">ROM 9:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:21\">1CO 1:21</a></p>\n<h3>In the church</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:1\">1CO 1:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:11\">1CO 12:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:28\">1CO 12:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:13\">PHP 2:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:1\">2TI 1:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:4\">HEB 2:4</a></p>",
